.Vb 3
\&        unknown, 8250, 16450, 16550, 16550A, Cirrus, 16650, 16650V2, 16750,
\&        16950, 16954, 16654, 16850, RSA, NS16550A, XSCALE, RM9000, OCTEON, AR7,
\&        U6_16550A
