\&        \-i      Ignore unprintable characters
\&        \-d      Dictionary order (blank or alphanumeric only)
\&        \-n      Sort numbers
\&        \-g      General numerical sort
\&        \-h      Sort human readable numbers (2K 1G)
\&        \-M      Sort month
\&        \-V      Sort version
