.IP \fBwc\fR 4
.IX Item "wc"
wc [\-cmlwL] [FILE]...
.Sp
Count lines, words, and bytes for FILEs (or stdin)
.Sp
.Vb 5
\&        \-c      Count bytes
\&        \-m      Count characters
\&        \-l      Count newlines
\&        \-w      Count words
\&        \-L      Print longest line length
.Ve
